{"tid":2066574,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"消委會：元氣、魚尚刺身驗出寄生蟲","createTime":"2020-06-16T11:10:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T12:01:08.000Z","uid":42734,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fb11c4a635842e6bcf871c77d58348b9dfb07977","tid":2066574,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:10:49.000Z","msg":"消委會檢測市面 50 款三文魚及吞拿魚刺身樣本，發現 49 款含有影響中樞神經系統的重金屬甲基汞。而在檢測的 19 款吞拿魚樣本中，有 10 款的含量更超出法例標準0.5ppm，超標最高的樣本來自荃灣爭鮮，甲基汞含量達1.48ppm，超標近兩倍。消委會亦分別在太古元氣壽司的吞拿魚刺身，以及荃灣魚尚的三文魚刺身，發現寄生蟲，其中元氣的吞拿魚樣本，同時發現蟲卵。"},{"pid":"586728704d5ceb322110d1d0685c20b44cfbb59e","tid":2066574,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:11:43.000Z","msg":"睇唔到"},{"pid":"5f693032842a24401721ff4de5a5872493819cbc","tid":2066574,"uid":33848,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:11:50.000Z","msg":"仲食元氣既人本身腦都有蟲"},{"pid":"54bccc968730ecf124c09f518764f47f0150988a","tid":2066574,"uid":66365,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:12:45.000Z","msg":"連登仔仲吹奏爭鮮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8436e995fc00ca7fda70af21b0fc92bf246d52f6","tid":2066574,"uid":216828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:17:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />藍屍rap"},{"pid":"b2b44886d4e32587e60c64442772689a525a4608","tid":2066574,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f693032842a24401721ff4de5a5872493819cbc","tid":2066574,"uid":33848,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:11:50.000Z","msg":"仲食元氣既人本身腦都有蟲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime"